high_descs: Turn around and go to stand in front of the stove.
Pick up the black pot from the stove.
Turn around and walk to stand in front of the fridge.
Put the pot in the fridge, close the door and then open it and take the pot out.
Turn around and go back to stand in front of the stove.
Put the pot on the bottom right of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled pot on the stove.

high_descs: Turn right, then turn right again to go to the stove.
Pick up the pot on the right side of the stove.
Go to the fridge behind you.
Chill the pot in the fridge.
Turn around and go back to the stove.
Place the pot on the front right range of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pot on the stove.

high_descs: Turn right, move a little bit forward, then turn right again, and head to the stove.
Pick up the black pot on the stove.
Turn right, move forward to the sink, then turn right and bring the pot to the fridge.
Chill the pot in the fridge.
Take the chilled put from the fridge, turn around and bring it back to the stove.
Put the chilled pot back on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pot on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around an walk up to the stove.
Pick up the black pot on the stove.
Turn around and walk up to the fridge.
But the black pot into the fridge to let it cool and then remove the pot from the fridge.
Turn around and walk back to the stove.
Place the black pot on the bottom right
anns.task_desc: To cool a pot as well as putting it back onto the stove.

high_descs: turn right thru the door, go forward a little bit, turn right and go to the stove.
pick up the big pot and turn to your right.
turn right again and go toward the fridge.
put the pot in the fridge and then wait, then  take it back out.
turn right, go forward, turn right again and go back to the stove.
put the pot back on the stove.
